Package: qgam
Type: Package
Title: Fit smooth additive quantile regression models
Version: 1.0
Date: 2016-6-01
Author: Matteo Fasiolo, Simon N. Wood, Yannig Goude, Raphael Nedellec.
Maintainer: Matteo Fasiolo <matteo.fasiolo@gmail.com>
Description: Fit smooth additive quantile regression models, mainly using a qgam() 
             function that is analogous to the gam() function in the mgcv package.
Details: See Fasiolo et al. (2016).
References: Fasiolo, M., Goude, Y., Nedellec, R. and Wood, S. N. (2016). 
            Fast calibrated additive quantile regression. 
            Available at https://github.com/mfasiolo/qgam/blob/master/draft_qgam.pdf.
License: GPL (>=2)
Depends:
    mgcv (>= 1.8.16)
Imports:
    shiny,
    plyr,
    doSNOW,
    parallel,
    grDevices
Suggests:
    knitr,
    MASS
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
